text: Chuyunchi-Chupanovo () is a rural locality (a selo) in Dmitriyevsky Selsoviet, Zilairsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 137 as of 2010. There are 3 streets. == Geography == It is located 43 km from Zilair, 15 km from Dmitriyevka. == References == Category:Rural localities in Zilairsky District
title: Chuyunchi-Chupanovo
